des:
If you have any problems, please contact us at Support@litmor.com

Litmor offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Amazon Alexa. Control your home lighting and other devices hands free. Just say the word, and Hello Litmor will make it happen.

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our Litmor APP in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on your Litmor devices and connect them with the Litmor app;
(4). IMPORTANT: In case you changed the name of your device on the Litmor APP, you will have to add this device to Amazon Echo again, as Amazon Echo will no longer recognize it;
(5). Download the Amazon Alexa app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Amazon Echo to the Amazon Alexa app;
(6). Open the Amazon Alexa APP and search the skill called "Litmor";
(7). Click‘enable skill of Litmor’, then input your account username and password 
(8). Say to Amazon Echo“Alexa, discover devices.”. Wait till Amazon Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now setup is completed. Try talking to Amazon Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands available for Hello Litmor:

Lights:
* Alexa, turn on livingroom light
* Alexa, turn off livingroom light
* Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent
Alarms:
* Alexa, turn on livingroom light alarm
* Alexa, turn off livingroom light alarm
